snippet.title: Megapatch II Official Trailer | SCP: Secret Laboratory
snippet.description:
The game has officially entered the last testing phase - Patreon tests!

Play the game for free: https://store.steampowered.com/app/700330/SCP_Secret_Laboratory/
Related article: https://steamcommunity.com/games/700330/announcements/detail/1613905115176601760
Web page: http://scpslgame.com
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/HubertMoszka

MTF voiced by:
Sam East (a.k.a. Doggdemon)
Twitch: twitch.tv/doggdemon
Twitter: @dogg_demon 

Music used:
-SCP:SL OST - Main Theme (Orchestral ver)
